U \in \tau_{X} \Rightarrow \exists B  
U = B \cap A = (B\cap Y) \cap A
U \in \tau_{Y}
U \in \tau_{Y} \Rightarrow \exists B  
U = B \cap A \Rightarrow \exists C 
 B = C \cap Y \Rightarrow U = (C \cap Y)\cap A = C \cap ( Y \cap A) = C \cap A.
